{"tid":1843744,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"極度懷疑林鄭係遊戲玩家，我哋只係data","createTime":"2020-01-26T10:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T10:56:48.000Z","uid":117332,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8540179da8a24219f0b31db3f18989f5f5996d46","tid":1843744,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"大家玩一啲管理城市/國家既遊戲，玩耐咗應該就會開始搞事，或者沖啲奇怪既成就。<br />\n<br />\n例如模擬市民會整千方百計玩死啲人仔<br />\n模擬遊樂園會整殺人機動遊戲<br />\n民主制度3 呢啲又會整死個城市<br />\n<br />\n甚至可能本身就玩緊一啲害人為目的既遊戲例如瘟疫公司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁就解釋到林鄭既行為，你做玩家會唔會用同情同對等既角度去睇啲遊戲data?(所以佢先當自己係神，自己做到幾on9都覺得自己岩哂) 你會唔會覺得有必要當data係人? (所以可以殺人唔貶眼)"},{"pid":"2b161ab137353bf14a77b3646fc61df70820ecbd","tid":1843744,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"free guy"},{"pid":"07faa226b818982ecdc2745dfaca2be955ee1376","tid":1843744,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"我諗大部分離地統治者都係咁"},{"pid":"f3823a08ecad8f47d586deab8656bae22744f4b8","tid":1843744,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"玩你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgS3ULF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgS3ULF.gif&h=ae661768&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb95ede53e9704d8e4be9cb3b22b399c2269ad73","tid":1843744,"uid":117332,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"成就解鎖:<br />\n倖存者        社會不滿度&gt;50%，超過6個月沒被暗殺<br />\n瘟疫傳播者         令香港武肺傳播率達99%<br />\n極權社會          香港極權指數&gt;80%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我解成就，應該會專攻呢啲要求，莫視其他指數(人權，經濟)。解完成就之後del save"},{"pid":"4f57c115871facf74ee0b324824a2a3c60879f02","tid":1843744,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"唔想比林鄭del save<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}